text:
East River, Manhattan shore, north from East 79th Street, showing the new fashionable East River residential area and preliminary construction on the East River Drive.

View 2 shows the area between East 81st and 82nd Streets, and view 3, buildings at E. 84th street.

P. L. Sperr

View 1,2: August, 1939
View 3: April, 1933

1442 C6 - NEG # 3055
title: East River - Manhattan shore - [Hagedorn Brothers Coal Company.]
